# Jiggon Algorithm: Safe Harbor
# A highly conservative algorithm that only trades in low-volatility environments.
# It ensures the ATR is low (stable market), the trend is defined, and momentum is positive
# but not overbought.

IF ATR < 1.0 AND MACD > 0.1 AND RSI < 60 AND EMA_TREND == BULLISH THEN BUY
IF ATR < 1.0 AND MACD < -0.1 AND RSI > 40 AND EMA_TREND == BEARISH THEN SELL
